<component id="ID_txt08">
  <text><![CDATA[<textformat blockindent="-14"><ul><li>Type 4 LSAs are used to advertise an ASBR to other areas and provide a route to the ASBR.</li><li>ABRs generate type 4 LSAs.</li><li>A type 4 LSA is generated by the originating ABR and regenerated by other ABRs.</li><li>A type 4 LSA link-state ID is identified by the router ID of the ASBR.</li></ui></textformat>]]></text> 
